data.description:
Lakefront home on a CUL-DE-SAC with a long driveway surrounded with beautiful palm trees!!!  A tropical home you have been looking for!!!
NEW ROOF AND HOT WATER HEATER!
Flex room has french doors and can be converted to 4th bedroom, office, or a living room.  Good size kitchen for entertaining and enough room for a good size island! Fenced backyard (Vinyl fence).  Large paved patio area for family gathering! CRAPE MYRTLES. Storage shed for yard equipment or kids bicycles, etc.
Home warranty available for one year for your peace of mind.
